ianship is resonating as pressures on reefs and lagoons from both development and climate change grow.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2027, \"end\": 2036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6496984050798375e-16, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an intimate knowledge\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2059}, {\"ngram\": \"the moana\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2072}, {\"ngram\": \"the ocean\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"the concept\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"guardianship\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2116}, {\"ngram\": \"pressures\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"reefs\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"lagoons\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2164}, {\"ngram\": \"both development\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2186}, {\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WAVE OF MANA Tereva David is also working with the local Teahupo'o community to embrace the Polynesian way of living in harmony with the environment.\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2306, \"end\": 2316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.84505248179367, \"rank\": 0.18062779365176826, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"WAVE\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2217}, {\"ngram\": \"MANA\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"Tereva David\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"the local Teahupo'o community\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2289}, {\"ngram\": \"harmony\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2340}, {\"ngram\": \"the environment\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the best to ride the Paris Olympic's ferocious wave in front of his village, David has run camps for promising young French Polynesian surfers for the past decade.\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2393, \"end\": 2398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999868609849, \"rank\": 1.3138795932171144e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2489, \"end\": 2495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9046736215642397, \"rank\": 0.10504022941035844, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2496, \"end\": 2506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.84505248179367, \"rank\": 0.18062779365176826, \"text\": \"Polynesian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2432}, {\"ngram\": \"his village\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"David\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2454}, {\"ngram\": \"camps\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2468}, {\"ngram\": \"the past decade\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"David, 35, teaches them respect - not just for the wave, but for themselves, for each other and for their culture and environment.\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2667, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"David\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2568}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2592}, {\"ngram\": \"their culture\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"environment\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My mom, when she was a little girl, she w