of the world's most powerful and alluring waves on their doorsteps fully benefited the village.\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"David\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3370}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3389}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's most powerful and alluring waves\", \"from\": 3425, \"to\": 3469}, {\"ngram\": \"their doorsteps\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3488}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Locals now provide surf camps, camera operators, taxi boats, and water safety patrols when top surfers come for big swells.\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3641, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Locals\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3524}, {\"ngram\": \"surf camps\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3547}, {\"ngram\": \"camera operators\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3565}, {\"ngram\": \"taxi boats\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3577}, {\"ngram\": \"water safety patrols\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3603}, {\"ngram\": \"top surfers\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\": 3620}, {\"ngram\": \"big swells\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It took us a long time but we finally did it.\", \"from\": 3643, \"to\": 3689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, nobody comes in and does it like the circus - we regulate,\\\" says David.\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nobody\", \"from\": 3695, \"to\": 3701}, {\"ngram\": \"the circus\", \"from\": 3728, \"to\": 3738}, {\"ngram\": \"David\", \"from\": 3760, \"to\": 3765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For us, it was the thing to do, to represent our mana, to represent our tupuna, our ancestors.\\\"\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3773, \"to\": 3775}, {\"ngram\": \"the thing\", \"from\": 3784, \"to\": 3793}, {\"ngram\": \"our mana\", \"from\"